This paper focuses on improving pre-training for natural language processing tasks, specifically by better representing and predicting spans of text. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses improvements in performance on various tasks, which suggests that it could also fall under categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
